  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/javafx/api/javafx/animation/Interpolator.html
  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/javafx/api/javafx/animation/KeyValue.html
  [4]: https://stackoverflow.com/a/38031826/230513
